data.title: New York Licensed Funeral Directors with Active Registrations
data.meta_description: New York Licensed Funeral Directors with Active Registrations
data.text:
Funeral directors must register their license with the New York State Department of Health on a biennial basis to work lawfully as a funeral director in New York State.

All registrations expire on June 30 of even years. This list will be updated monthly.
